  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of RV4104A Ointment in Onychomycosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Parallel-Group, Multicentre, Open-Labelled, Active-Controlled Study to Assess the Efficacy, Safety and Tolerability of RV4104A Ointment Versus Bifonazole-Urea Ointment for the Complete Removal of the Clinically Infected Nail Plate Area in Patients With Toenail Onychomycosis</official_title>
