  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the efficacy of RV4104A ointment versus
      bifonazole-urea ointment for the complete removal of the clinically infected nail plate area
      in patients with toenail onychomycosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
